{{Taxobox | image = | image_caption= | domain = [[Bacteria]] | phylum = [[Elusimicrobia]] | classis = [[Blastocatellia]] | ordo = [[Blastocatellales]] | familia = [[Blastocatellaceae]] | genus = ''[[Aridibacter]]'' | species = '''''A. nitratireducens''''' | binomial = ''Aridibacter nitratireducens'' | binomial_authority = Huber et al. 2017<ref name=Aridibacter-nitratireducens>{{cite journal |last1=Parte |first1=A.C. |title=Aridibacter |journal=www.bacterio.net |url=http://www.bacterio.net/aridibacter.html}}</ref> | type_strain = A_24_SHP_-5_238, CECT 9235, DSM 102177<ref name=UniProt>{{cite journal |title=Aridibacter nitratireducens |journal=www.uniprot.org |url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/1911421 |language=en}}</ref> | subdivision = | synonyms = }}
'''''Aridibacter nitratireducens''''' is a non-motile bacterium from the genus of ''[[Aridibacter]]'' which has been isolated from clayey sand from [[Eikwe]] in [[Ghana]].<ref name=Aridibacter-nitratireducens/><ref name=UniProt/><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Parker |first1=Charles Thomas |last2=Garrity |first2=George M |title=Taxonomic Abstract for the species. |journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts |date=1 January 2003 |doi=10.1601/tx.30970 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Details: DSM-102177 |journal=www.dsmz.de |url=https://www.dsmz.de/catalogues/details/culture/DSM-102177.html |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Huber |first1=KJ |last2=Geppert |first2=AM |last3=Groß |first3=U |last4=Luckner |first4=M |last5=Wanner |first5=G |last6=Cooper |first6=P |last7=Abakah |first7=J |last8=Janssen |first8=I |last9=Overmann |first9=J |title=Aridibacter nitratireducens sp. nov., a member of the family Blastocatellaceae, class Blastocatellia, isolated from an African soil. |journal=International journal of systematic and evolutionary microbiology |date=November 2017 |volume=67 |issue=11 |pages=4487-4493 |doi=10.1099/ijsem.0.002318 |pmid=28945537}}</ref>
